summary: I'm currently studying at TUDelft, MSc in Roboitcs. Got my Bachelor of Engineering in Robotics Engineering at SUSTech. I has worked as an undergraduate researcher under the supervision of Professor Chenglong Fu at the Department of Mechanical and Energy Engineering at SUSTech. My main interest lies in legged robots and human-enhancing robots.
